zookeeper:
监控命令：root@Io:/service/zookeeper# run
exec 2>&1
exec /root/distributed/zookeeper/bin/zkServer.sh start

启动命令：supervise /service/zookeeper



storm:

运行：/distributed/storm-0.7.2# 
命令配置的：
export STORM_HOME=/usr/local/storm-0.7.4
export PATH=$PATH:$STORM_HOME/bin


把每一个服务器上的/etc/hosts
10.0.0.21       Io
10.0.0.22       Ganymade


